board.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Flurry</span><hr size=1> It has nothing to do with your weapon at all just your CDW spec and is suppose to be non-resistible.  <p><U><A HREF=http://www.camelotherald.com/realms/Kay/>Hibernia/Kay</A> - <A HREF=http://www.camelotherald.com/guilds/guild.php?s=Kay&g=238>Storm's Fury</A></U>
